## Component Architecture Plan

### 1. NorthwesternFilteringSystem.js (Main Component)
**Purpose**: Primary filtering interface with real-time visual feedback
**Key Features**:
- Northwestern category filtering with visual pie chart previews
- Coverage level filtering (0/1/2) with clinical context
- Multi-category combination filtering
- Clinical scenario quick filters
- Real-time highlighting of matching antibiotics
- Filter persistence for clinical workflow

**Integration Points**:
- Consumes Agent 3.1's spatial layout for visual feedback
- Uses Agent 3.2's group organization for contextual filtering
- Provides filtered results to spatial layout for highlighting

### 2. northwesternFilterLogic.js (Utilities)
**Purpose**: Core filtering algorithms and logic
**Key Features**:
- Real-time filter application (<100ms response)
- Combination therapy filtering
- Text search with medical terminology
- Filter state management and persistence
- Performance optimization for clinical workflow

### 3. FilterControlPanel.js (UI Components)
**Purpose**: User interface controls for filtering
**Key Features**:
- Northwestern segment selector with pie chart previews  
- Coverage level sliders with clinical context
- Quick filter buttons for common scenarios
- Filter history and saved sets
- Mobile-optimized touch controls

### 4. clinicalScenarioFilters.js (Medical Logic)
**Purpose**: Pre-defined clinical scenario filtering
**Key Features**:
- ICU sepsis filters (broad empiric coverage)
- Outpatient UTI filters (oral agents, gram-negative)
- MRSA coverage filters
- Post-surgical prophylaxis filters
- Emergency protocol filters (<30 second access)
- Resistance pattern warnings

## Northwestern Filtering Specifications

### Category Filters (8 segments)
```javascript
const NORTHWESTERN_CATEGORIES = {
  MRSA: { name: 'MRSA', color: '#d32f2f', priority: 'high' },
  VRE_faecium: { name: 'VRE faecium', color: '#7b1fa2', priority: 'high' },
  anaerobes: { name: 'Anaerobes', color: '#388e3c', priority: 'medium' },
  atypicals: { name: 'Atypicals', color: '#1976d2', priority: 'medium' },
  pseudomonas: { name: 'Pseudomonas', color: '#f57c00', priority: 'high' },
  gramNegative: { name: 'Gram Negative', color: '#5d4037', priority: 'medium' },
  MSSA: { name: 'MSSA', color: '#0288d1', priority: 'low' },
  enterococcus_faecalis: { name: 'E. faecalis', color: '#689f38', priority: 'low' }
};
```

### Coverage Levels
- **0 (None)**: No coverage - excluded from results
- **1 (Moderate)**: Some coverage - shown with visual indication
- **2 (Good)**: Good coverage - prioritized in results

### Clinical Scenarios
```javascript
const CLINICAL_SCENARIOS = {
  icuSepsis: {
    name: 'ICU Sepsis',
    filters: { MRSA: 1, pseudomonas: 1, gramNegative: 2 },
    description: 'Broad empiric coverage for severe sepsis'
  },
  outpatientUTI: {
    name: 'Outpatient UTI',
    filters: { gramNegative: 2 },
    routeFilter: ['red', 'purple'], // PO or both
    description: 'Oral agents for uncomplicated UTI'
  },
  mrsaCoverage: {
    name: 'MRSA Coverage',
    filters: { MRSA: 2 },
    description: 'All agents with good MRSA activity'
  },
  postSurgical: {
    name: 'Post-surgical Prophylaxis',
    cellWallActive: true,
    filters: { MSSA: 2, gramNegative: 1 },
    description: 'Cell wall active agents for surgical prophylaxis'
  }
};
```

## Performance Contracts

### Target Performance Metrics
- **Filter Application**: <100ms for real-time interaction
- **Visual Feedback**: <50ms for highlighting updates
- **UI Responsiveness**: <200ms for control interactions
- **Emergency Mode**: <30 seconds for urgent clinical decisions
- **Mobile Performance**: Optimized for clinical tablets

### Memory Management
- Efficient filter state caching
- Lazy loading of complex filter combinations
- Debounced search input
- Virtualized result lists for large datasets

## Integration Specifications for Agent 3.4

### API Contracts
```javascript
// Filter state interface
interface FilterState {
  northwesternCategories: { [key: string]: { enabled: boolean, minCoverage: number } };
  clinicalScenario: string | null;
  textSearch: string;
  routeFilter: string[];
  cellWallActiveOnly: boolean;
  emergencyMode: boolean;
}

// Filter result interface  
interface FilterResult {
  matchingAntibiotics: AntibioticData[];
  highlightedPositions: GridPosition[];
  filterSummary: FilterSummary;
  performanceMetrics: PerformanceMetrics;
}
```

### Performance Optimization Hooks
- `useFilterPerformance()` - Performance monitoring
- `useFilterCache()` - Result caching
- `useFilterDebounce()` - Input debouncing
- `useEmergencyMode()` - Emergency optimizations

### Mobile Optimization Requirements
- Touch-friendly filter controls (44px minimum)
- Swipe gestures for filter categories
- Responsive filter panel layout
- Haptic feedback for filter selection
- Voice search integration for hands-free operation

