## Risk Mitigation

### Performance Risks
- Complex multi-filter combinations may exceed 100ms target
- Large dataset filtering on mobile devices
- Memory usage with multiple cached filter states

### Mitigation Strategies
- Filter complexity analysis and optimization
- Progressive enhancement for mobile
- Intelligent cache eviction policies
- Background worker for complex calculations

### Medical Accuracy Risks
- Filter combinations may produce clinically inappropriate suggestions
- Northwestern methodology compliance

### Mitigation Strategies
- Medical validation for all clinical scenarios
- Clear disclaimers for educational use
- Northwestern methodology adherence verification
- Expert clinical review of filter logic

